INSERT INTO `event` VALUES ('16', '南山体质检测与运动健康指导', '9', '大热篮球俱乐部', '1', '2', '0', '', '亲子教育', '[{\"name\":\"幼儿体测（团体）\",\"price\":\"25\"},{\"name\":\"学生体测（团体）\",\"price\":\"25\"},{\"name\":\"成年体测（团体）\",\"price\":\"125\"},{\"name\":\"肥胖检测\",\"price\":\"50\"},{\"name\":\"人体成分检测\",\"price\":\"150\"},{\"name\":\"骨密度检测\",\"price\":\"150\"},{\"name\":\"动脉硬化检测\",\"price\":\"250\"},{\"name\":\"生长发育测评\",\"price\":\"150\"},{\"name\":\"身高预测\",\"price\":\"150\"},{\"name\":\"性格特点检测\",\"price\":\"150\"},{\"name\":\"专注力测评\",\"price\":\"150\"},{\"name\":\"动作神经综合反应\",\"price\":\"550\"},{\"name\":\"体育天赋测评\",\"price\":\"450\"},{\"name\":\"心脏功能风险评估\",\"price\":\"500\"},{\"name\":\"室内有氧跑运动指导\",\"price\":\"500\"},{\"name\":\"测试数据U盘\",\"price\":\"80\"},{\"name\":\"专家咨询指导\",\"price\":\"200\"},{\"name\":\"中考跑长短跑满分指导\",\"price\":\"250\"}]', '2', '25', '0', '', '0', 'Hot Basketball 1', '3', '1515373200', '1546941600', '0', '0', '广东省', '深圳市', '南山区', '深圳市南山区桂庙西路与月亮湾大道交汇处（阳光文体中心二楼）', '1000', '1', '<div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>南山体质检测与运动健康指导</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>南山体质测定与运动健身指导站由广东省体育局审批建立。指导站内配置有较先进的检测仪器与设备，为幼儿、学生、成年人、老年人、企事业单位员工进行体质测定、人体成分测评、骨密度测试、动脉硬化检测、生长发育测评、身高预测、体育天赋测评、性格特点检测、动作神经综合反应检测、中考体育满分训练指导、运动风险评估、靶心率有氧跑运动指导、运动与营养处方、科学运动指导与咨询等系列专业服务</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a5342829b304.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>体质检测</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>幼儿体测</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>身高、体重、坐位体前屈、网球掷远、10米折返跑、平衡木、立定跳远、双脚连续跳</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a545d267604e.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>学生体测</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>身高、体重、握力、坐位体前屈、台阶测试、肺活量、立定跳远、背力、50米跑</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a543310599af.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a54336bdc3d2.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>成年体测</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>身高、体重、握力、坐位体前屈、台阶测试、肺活量、纵跳、闭眼单足力、选择反应时、仰卧起坐（女）、俯卧撑（男）</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a5433edac925.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a54340c8c06f.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>老年体测</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>血压、身高、体重、握力、坐位体前屈、肺活量、闭眼单足立、选择反应时</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a5434641f34e.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a54347e1d922.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>肥胖检测</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>血压、身高、体重、腰围、臀围、腰臀比、脉压差、BMI指数</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a543553b0882.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a54356dd47a4.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>人体成分检测</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>脂肪含量、肌肉含量、脂肪比率、健康评估</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a5435ef2a84e.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>骨密度检测</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>成、老年人骨（钙）量检测</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a5437b7c821f.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a5437c1dda7d.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>动脉硬化检测</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>血管硬度（baPWV）变化、血管堵塞（ABI）程度检测</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a54380c89439.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a543818607a6.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>生长、身高发育测评</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>《中华05》骨龄测评与评定</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a54395d9b79e.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a54388681bd8.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>性格特点（神经类型）</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>灵活性、稳定型、兴奋型、中间型、易扰型、谨慎型、泛散型、抑制型、模糊型</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a54397ec77d8.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a54398414fb1.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>动作神经综合反应</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>光反应、声反应、选择反应、综合反应</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a543a2a11b72.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>体育天赋测评</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>身高、体重、指距、上肢长、肩宽、骼宽、肺活量、台阶测试、握力、背力、立定跳远、坐位体前屈、羽毛球掷远、10X4往返</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a543ad1c1d45.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a543ade6e95d.png\" style=\"padding-top:5px\"></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><h5>中考200米/800米/1000米满分训练指导</h5></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><p>用计算训练法指导训练</p></div><div class=\"operationDiv\"><img class=\"desimg\" src=\"/uploads/images/event/2018/01/5a543